"Shows the results of Object rotation when the pivot point is set to "
"Bounding Box."
msgstr "显示轴心点设置为“边界框”时物体旋转的结果。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:50
msgid "Multiple objects."
msgstr "多个物体。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:52
msgid ""
"Shows the location of the Bounding Box (left) pivot point compared to "
"the Median Point (right)."
msgstr "显示边界框（左）轴心点与质心点（右）相比较的位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:56
msgid "In Edit Mode"
msgstr "在编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:58
msgid ""
"This time it is the Object Data that is enclosed in the bounding box. "
"The bounding box in *Edit Mode* takes no account of the Object(s) "
"origins, only the center of the selected vertices."
msgstr ""
"这一次是包围在边界框中的物体数据。 *编辑模式* 中的边界框不考虑物体的原"
"点，只考虑所选顶点的中心。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/bounding_box_center.rst:64
msgid ""
"The effects of rotation in different mesh selection modes when the "
"bounding box is set as the pivot point. The pivot point is shown by a "
"yellow circle."
msgstr ""
"当边界框被设置为轴心点时，不同网格选择模式下的旋转效果。轴心点用黄色圆圈"
"表示。"

